    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement. The powertrain remains robust, with individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response and a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Handling is sharpened via a factory-spec M-tuned suspension and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is superlative, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
