      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been treated with care. The exterior paint maintains a high-quality shine, with only a few minor stone chips consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seating shows light, natural character lines but remains supple and free of any punctures or thinning. All power features, from the sunroof to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, responsive engine. We have recently performed a full oil service and brake pad replacement, ensuring it is ready for the road from day one. This is a well-rounded, dependable vehicle that offers premium comfort without the premium price tag of a showroom-new model.",
